## What It Is

Google CodeWiki transforms any GitHub repo into an interactive knowledge base:
- Auto-generated docs from code (every PR regenerates relevant sections)
- Architecture diagrams (auto-drawn from code structure)
- AI chatbot powered by Gemini that knows your codebase
- Links back to source: doc → function definition in one click
- Free for public repos

